    </div>
</div>

<div class="features">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>✅ Dynamic page rendering with EJS</li>
        <li>✅ Add and manage items</li>
        <li>✅ Responsive design</li>
        <li>✅ RESTful API endpoints</li>
        <li>✅ Clean and modern UI</li>
        <li>✅ Easy to extend</li>
    </ul>
